# Design Document: Matasree Store Bug Fixes

## Overview

This document provides the concrete implementation design for 21 confirmed bugs and broken features in the Matasree Store. Fixes are grouped by category and presented with exact file paths, before/after code snippets where clarifying, and rationale for each change. No new npm dependencies are introduced; all fixes use existing patterns already present in the codebase.

